# reprepro runtime options (US-015).
#
# `verbose` — echo each operation to stdout so CI logs show the package
# names being added and the Release-file regeneration.
#
# We deliberately do NOT set `basedir` here — the workflow passes it
# explicitly via `reprepro -b ./staging/apt`, which keeps this config
# location-independent (works the same on a maintainer's laptop under a
# different path).

verbose
